item.title: CVE-2021-36870|2024-08-04T01:01:59.812Z -- code%20cabin%20inc -- wp%20google%20maps%20%28wordpress%20plugin%29
item.description: Multiple Authenticated Persistent Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) vulnerabilities in WordPress WP Google Maps plugin (versions <= 8.1.12). Vulnerable parameters: &dataset_name, &wpgmza_gdpr_retention_purpose, &wpgmza_gdpr_company_name, &name #2, &name, &polyname #2, &polyname, &address.
